data.description: Welcome to this exquisite single-owner home nestled in the gated Stone Oak neighborhood of Panther Creek. Boasting a thoughtful design, this residence offers a MASTER BEDROOM AND BATHROOM DOWNSTAIRS, complemented by a separate guest bathroom for added convenience. Embrace the tranquility as the home backs up to a PRIVATELY OWNED 65-ACRE RANCH, granting unparalleled serenity. Enjoy enhanced privacy to the left of the house thanks to a concrete French drain. Discover a vast upstairs loft, perfect for crafting an office, playroom, or second living area to suit your lifestyle. The expansive kitchen is complete with a generous island and dining area. Experience comfort, space, and a seamless blend of indoor-outdoor living in this remarkable abode.
